    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Actually no, that's not the problem.\nI gave stealth generator `TargetableUnit` and removed `TargetableBuilding`, no change.\n\nWhat I noticed when testing against an AI (with shroud/fog disabled) that I could target vehicles, but NOT the construction yard as long as they were not stealthed. As soon as the stealth gen was placed, the vehicles became untargetable, while the cyard suddenly became targetable.\n\nI suspect there's actually something wrong with the visibility check of actors with a footprint.\n"
