    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Seems like the target (Stealth Generator) is considered a `FrozenActor` (which sounds quite wrong, given the screenshot below). Source is `UnitOrderTargeter.GetCursor() - var underCursor`. This eventually gets to `AttackBase.CanTarget()`, which has no problems with frozen actors and that results in a `UnitOrderResult` being dispatched successfully for that target.\n\n![](http://i.imgur.com/qTnUo8A.png)\n"
